sequenceDiagram
    actor U as 用户
    participant C as Coordinator
    participant TD as TaskDecomposer
    participant HM as HermesAdapter
    participant HMB as Hermes ACP Broker<br/>tcp://127.0.0.1:9001
    participant CL as ClaudeAdapter
    participant CLA as Claude API<br/>anthropic.com/v1/messages
    participant OC as OpenClawAdapter
    participant OCG as OpenClaw Gateway<br/>ws://127.0.0.1:18679
    participant RM as ResultMerger

    U->>C: "审查这个函数的 SQL 注入风险"
    C->>TD: decompose(request)
    TD->>C: SubTask[] + Plan (1 stage, 3 parallel)

    Note over C: === PARALLEL STAGE ===

    par Hermes 静态分析
        C->>HM: task_request(sub-1, analyst)
        HM->>HMB: ACP TASK_ASSIGN
        Note right of HMB: 延迟 1600ms
        HMB->>HM: ACP TASK_RESULT
        HM->>C: task_result(静态分析, score=0.92)
    and Claude 安全扫描
        C->>CL: task_request(sub-2, security_scanner)
        CL->>CLA: HTTP POST
        Note right of CLA: 延迟 2200ms
        CLA->>CL: HTTP 200 + SSE
        CL->>C: task_result(漏洞扫描, score=0.94)
    and OpenClaw 测试生成
        C->>OC: task_request(sub-3, tester)
        OC->>OCG: WebSocket req
        Note right of OCG: 延迟 1500ms
        OCG->>OC: WebSocket res
        OC->>C: task_result(测试用例, score=0.88)
    end

    Note over C: === MERGE (voting_dedup) ===
    C->>RM: merge(strategy=voting_dedup)
    RM->>C: mergedOutput + finalScore=91.3%<br/>conflicts=1 (majority_wins)

    C->>U: 合并审查报告
